description:
Create src/components/tick-create-dialog.ts using Shoelace sl-dialog:

@customElement('tick-create-dialog')
export class TickCreateDialog extends LitElement {
  @property({ type: Boolean }) open = false;
  @property({ type: Array }) epics: string[] = [];
}

Form fields using Shoelace:
- sl-input: title (required)
- sl-textarea: description
- sl-select: type (task, epic, bug, feature, chore)
- sl-select: priority (0-4 with labels)
- sl-select: parent epic (optional, from epics list)
- sl-input: labels (comma-separated)
- sl-checkbox: manual task

Buttons:
- Cancel: closes dialog, resets form
- Create: validates, calls createTick API, emits 'tick-created' with new tick

Test: Open dialog, fill form, submit, verify API called with correct data
